details.summary: <rev> Optimize FullyQualifiedChannelResolver. If the repCap is the same as previous one, we don't need to resolve it again because previous result is stored in FullyQualifiedChannelResolver.
<rev> Refine the constructor of PinMapInitializer to take in vector of std::string, rather than vector of const char*, this could save us some trouble to do the conversion when using this class.

[Feedback collect]<rev>This is a review to collect feedback about how to add .NET support for DCPower Channel Expansion and Unsync-operation feature. You can find summary in this file. For more details, you can refer to the discussion at "DCPower .NET API" channel in Teams.
[Submitted] <rev> [1/4] Merge PinMap and MultiInstrumentPinMap into one class: make pinmaptools::PinMap class able to work with pinmap with multiple instruments
[submitted][.NET API]<rev>Add Control related xxxChannels APIs to NI-DCPower .NET API. We want to support channel-based operation for these APIs to Channel Expansion.

[Submitted] <rev> Ignore the error that thrown by closeChildSessions(). To call self-test, Self Calibrate and Reset Device for CXP sessions, we close the single channel child sessions and create new child sessions that are grouped by device.
[submitted][.NET API]<rev>Add GetChannelName, GetChannelNameString to NI-DCPower .NET API. They will be used by the unit test of other APIs, so I'd like to add them first before other APIs.
[Submitted]<rev> Rename the numChannels to numberOfChannels
[Submitted] <rev> [4/4] Merge PinMap and MultiInstrumentPinMap into one class: add new error code to pinmaptools
[Submitted] <rev> [3/3] Change to use a factory to create ImporterExporter when calling import/export functions of Session: Remove setImporterExporter() from Session.h.mako and Session.cpp.mako
[Submitted] <rev> [1/3] Change to use a factory to create ImporterExporter when calling import/export functions of Session: Add ImporterExporterFactory to niScopeCXP.
[Submitted] <rev> [2/3] Change to use a factory to create ImporterExporter when calling import/export functions of Session: Add ImporterExporterFactory to nidcpowerCXP.
[submitted][.NET API]<rev>Add all channel-based APIs to internal implementation. I'd like to put them together.
[submitted]<rev> Clean up the implementation of HramCache private method "cacheHramPins".
[submitted]<rev> [1/2] Encapsulate the logic for parsing HRAM pin list: merge two functions in PinMapExpertInterface to one which is used to parse HRAM pin list.
[submitted]<rev> [2/2] Encapsulate the logic for parsing HRAM pin list: retrofit the implementation of PinMapExpert and its unit tests because of interface changes in Part1.
[submitted]<rev> Clean up the implementation of HramCache public method "initialize".
[Submitted] <rev> [2/4] Merge PinMap and MultiInstrumentPinMap into one class: retrofit niDigitalPB

[Submitted] <rev>[Part 4/4] Enable out of process debugging for session created by initialize with independent channels: Add shared utility functions to handle remoteDebugOptionsString.
[submitted]<rev> [2/2] Clean up HramCache interface: retrofit HramCache implementation because of interface changes in Part1.
[submitted]<rev> To follow our code convention: rename "siteNum" to "siteNumber" and change the type to "uint32_t" in HramCache class.
<rev> [1/2] Let client choose if it need to reset when initialize child sessions each time openChildSessions() is called.
<rev> [2/2] Let client choose if it need to reset when initialize child sessions each time openChildSessions() is called.
<rev> Add error elaboration in AutoSession when initializing/closing child session fails.

<rev> [2/3] Export correct global attribute value when the attribute is set in both single point mode and advanced sequence: add dcpowerCXP-specific ImporterExporter.

[.NET API]<rev>Add Software Trigger related xxxWithChannels APIs to NI-DCPower .NET API. We want to support channel-based operation for these APIs to Channel Expansion.
<rev> Remove outdated TODO.
[.NET API]<rev>Codegen the functions in nidcpowerPrivate.h, since we want to add .NET support for GetSessionState which stays in that file.
[.NET API]<rev>Add Digital Trigger related xxxWithChannels APIs to NI-DCPower .NET API. We want to support channel-based operation for these APIs to Channel Expansion.
<rev> Fix a bug of PAL device that host session cann't restore to running state if debug session requests privilege after host session initiated.
<rev>Move DiscoverCurrentRanges and GetNextInstructionSequence from nidcpowerPrivate.h to nidcpowerLV.h, since these functions use lvdatacov, which should stay in nidcpowerLV.h.
<rev> [1/2] single source the error handling for cxp plugin's LV init() and close(): Add two utility macros in cxp.
<rev>[2/2] Single source the error handling for cxp plugin's LV init() and close(): Retrofit niDigitalCXP, nidcpowerCXP, niScopeCXP to apply the new macros in cxp for LV entry points.

<rev> Implement niDCPowerCXP_GetLiveMeasurements. This function has a parameter "void* reserved", which is difficult to code-gen based on currently implementation of mergers. There's no way to write a new merger to support this parameter, when we don't know the size of  "void* reserved".
<rev> Optimize FullyQualifiedChannelResolver. If the repCap is the same as previous one, we don't need to resolve it again because previous result is stored in FullyQualifiedChannelResolver.
<rev> Refine the constructor of PinMapInitializer to take in vector of std::string, rather than vector of const char*, this could save us some trouble to do the conversion when using this class.
